name: Building A Technical Ecosystem
description:
It's our maiden event Yaay!, come let's build together as we connect, collaborate and share resources. GDG Ojo-Festac is thriving to build a functional technical ecosystem: one that is fluid, intentional and inclusive.

There will be a host of amazing speakers ready to inspire and motivate you into doing more.

We hope that with this event the aftermath would be one of tremendous importance as part of our agenda to Building A Technical Ecosystem in Ojo and Festac regions.
